      <title>黎巴嫩外交官获得多数票，当选总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/lebanese-diplomat-secures-majority-vote-for-prime-minister-role</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黎巴嫩外交官、前联合国特使、现任国际法院院长纳瓦夫·萨拉姆已获得成为该国总理所需的票数。]]></description>
