    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦反对派不会阻止延长总统任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/zimbabwe-opposition-won-t-block-bid-to-extend-president-s-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦主要反对党表示，不会阻止要求总统埃默森·姆南加古瓦将任期延长两年至 2030 年的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/zimbabwe-opposition-won-t-block-bid-to-extend-president-s-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:24:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克立法者选举塔拉帕为新议长，抗议活动再度爆发</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/mozambique-lawmakers-elect-talapa-new-speaker-as-protests-resume</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克议会周一选举玛格丽达·塔拉帕为新任议长，反对党为抗议存在争议的十月选举而拒绝出席就职典礼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/mozambique-lawmakers-elect-talapa-new-speaker-as-protests-resume</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:16:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默对里夫斯“充满信心”，强调财政规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/starmer-has-full-confidence-in-reeves-stresses-fiscal-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，他对财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯“充满信心”，并强调英国政府将坚持财政规则，以应对英国借贷成本飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/starmer-has-full-confidence-in-reeves-stresses-fiscal-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:12:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国极右翼与特朗普站在同一阵线，反对风能</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/german-far-right-aligns-with-trump-on-takedown-of-wind-energy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国极右翼选择党警告称，一旦赢得政权，将拆除风力发电场，这引发了该国能源行业的强烈反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/german-far-right-aligns-with-trump-on-takedown-of-wind-energy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 12:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大亨支持的公司被敦促出售南非新鲜食品部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/tycoon-backed-firm-urged-to-sell-south-african-fresh-food-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非反垄断监管机构建议亿万富翁帕特里斯·莫塞佩 (Patrice Motsepe) 支持的非洲彩虹资本 (African Rainbow Capital) 撤资该国最大的新鲜农产品机构之一，因为它阻碍了竞争。]]></description>
